official_title: A bill to provide for the amendment of the public survey records to eliminate a conflict between the official cadastral survey and a private survey of the so-called Wold Tract within the Medicine Bow National Forest, Wyoming.

summary.text: Requires the amendment of the public survey records to eliminate a conflict between the official cadastral survey and a private survey of the so-called Wold Tract within the Medicine Bow National Forest, Wyoming.
